ai_analysis.timeline: The risk is consistently low throughout the week due to minimal precipitation. However, areas near water bodies may experience localized flooding if water levels rise for other reasons not captured in the precipitation forecast.
recommendations: Monitor water levels in nearby water bodies.
Maintain drainage systems to ensure efficient water runoff.
Alert local residents about the proximity to water bodies.
